4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer", which is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge of AI or Machine Learning. The course aims to prepare students for a career as a data scientist and provides hands-on experience in building ML models. The duration of the course is 16 weeks, with 3 classes held weekly. The class size is limited to 12 people, ensuring personalized attention. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will also learn about algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. Additionally, students will have the opportunity to practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop